<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وقول الله تعالى:</span> فَأُهْلِكُوا بِالطّااغِيَةِ <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
